data.description: HIGHLY DESIRABLE LOCATION & CONVENIENT to I-35 with lots of Shopping & Restaurants Nearby in Popular Downtown Burleson. MOVE IN JUST IN TIME TO CELEBRATE THE HOLIDAYS! Plus Only 25 Minutes from Downtown Fort Worth. Lovely One Story Brick 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home situated on a Spacious Treed Lot in an established neighborhood. Home features Central Air & Heat with Neutral Colors throughout with a large covered patio overlooking the treed backyard with a nice size storage shed. Floorplan features Large bedrooms with carpet throughout and tile in bathrooms, kitchen & breakfast areas. Move in Ready and can close Quickly if Buyer desires. Don't miss out on this AFFORDABLE HOME. MUST SEE!
